comment: Smith (PHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Mudiay (DEN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Landry (PHI) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Covington (PHI) makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Arthur (DEN) legally contests Smith's (PHI) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Landry (PHI) makes contact with Harris's (DEN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
McConnell (PHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Mudiay (DEN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Grant (PHI) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests Mudiay's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Arthur (DEN) commits a take foul on Covington (PHI).
Harris (DEN) commits a take foul on Covington (PHI).
Philadelphia does not line up for the Free Throw attempts in a timely manner.
McConnell (PHI) cleanly strips the ball from Mudiay (DEN).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Mudiay's (DEN) shot was released prior to the clock expiring was upheld.
